window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A young teacher's life is turned upside down when fate brings her face-to-face with the massive bear shifter she's destined to be with forever.</b></p> <p><b>Tristian</b></p> <p>As a bear shifter, I never expected to find my fated mate in a radical human bar, but one whiff of her sweet vanilla scent and I knew she was mine. Now I'll fight heaven and hell to claim Ebony and make her see that she belongs with me in Wintermoon forever.</p> <p><b>Ebony</b></p> <p>My quiet life is upended when Tristian, a massive bear shifter, bursts into the radical bar where I'm reluctantly on a date and declares I'm his fated mate. He's determined to chase me down and whisk me away to the supernatural haven of Wintermoon, but can I trust this primal stranger who's so intent on chasing me down?</p> <p><i>Wintermoon Shorts is a series set in the world of Wintermoon, featuring characters from the Fated Mates series. These stories focus less on plot and more on spicy moments. For mature listeners.</i></p>"; 
